-- Illinois jury reaches verdict in Merck Vioxx case
-- 
-- Tue Mar 27, 2007 10:53am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/03/27/us-merck-vioxx-jury-idUSWAA00009120070327

 

 EDWARDSVILLE, Illinois  (Reuters) - A jury has reached a verdict in a case against Merck & Co. ( MRK.N ) brought by an Illinois man who blamed the company's Vioxx painkiller in the death of his 52-year-old wife. 

 The verdict was expected to be read in court shortly.